        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Use a ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Snippet",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " directive to embed a code example from the project’s “Snippets” directory on the page.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "The ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "path",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " argument is the relative path from the package’s top-level “Snippets” directory to your snippet file without the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : ".swift",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " extension.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code" : [
            "@Snippet(path: \"example-snippet\", slice: \"setup\")"
          ],
          "syntax" : "markdown",
          "type" : "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "If you prefer, you can specify the relative path from the package’s ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "root",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text" : " directory (by including a “Snippets\/” prefix).",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "You can also include the package name—as defined in ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Package.swift",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : "—before the “Snippets\/” prefix.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Neither of these leading path components are necessary because all your snippet code files are always located in your package’s “Snippets” directory.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content" : [
