                },
                {
                  "text" : "Before Swift-DocC 6.2.1, the ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "code" : "@Snippet",
                  "type" : "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " path needed to include both the package name component and the “Snippets” component:",
